            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Use a WHOIS lookup (whois.icann.org, domaintools.com, or the whois command) to see the original registration date. Alternatively, the Wayback Machine at web.archive.org shows the earliest indexed snapshot, which can reveal when a domain actually became active.</p></div></div>
          </div>
